              <h2 class="richPinName">
               <a class="richPinNameLink" href="http://www.countrycleaver.com/2013/02/caramel-macchiato-cookies.html" rel="nofollow">
                Caramel Macchiato Cookies
               </a>
              </h2>
              <div class="richPinSourceWrapper">
               <a class="richPinSourceLink" href="http://www.countrycleaver.com/2013/02/caramel-macchiato-cookies.html" rel="nofollow">
                <img class="richPinSourceFavicon" src="https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/favicons/7e90697c14fa8eb23eca30720cad3de214a9143b3b7ce18a760e0fc6.ico?6773ff4ef285ca6b9cf342092b51e284"/>
                Country Cleaver
               </a>
              </div>
              <div class="richPinMeta ">
               <div class="richPinArticleSummary">
                You favorite Starbucks drink in caramel macchiato cookie! Coffee flavored cookies with caramel sauce drizzled over the top.
               </div>
